/h Criteria For Success That need to be demonstrated /h

This program must be able to organize the client’s events
 The program should be able to alert the client about each event they have
Notifications should be able to be sent without the client needing to open the program
 The user should be able to input their events
The user should be able to input the date and time of their events
 The user should be able to prioritize their events accordingly
The program should be able to display which events are occuring that day
 The program should be able to store the memory of the events inputted
The program should be able to organize the events by categories given by the user
Ie. Homework would go in the ‘School’ category
The program should be able to save the events inputted even when the program close
